@nassia_g Hello Nassia,
unfortunately we are not able to accelerate the waiting time on our hotlines. Our colleagues are doing their best to work as fast as possible to shorten waiting times. 
Best regards, Alessandra

@flannel_joe Hi Erin,
Thank you for getting in touch. Please send us your booking code via PM, so we can take a closer look.
Best regards, Shawn

@stevedurrant10 Hi Steve,
We apologize for the long wait. Due to the large number of inquiries that we are currently receiving you may experience longer waiting times. Send us your booking code as PM, so we can assist you further.
Best regards, Shawn

@makyjen Hello Jen,
we are so sorry for the inconvenience and totally understand your frustration. Be assured that the luggage will be delivered as soon as possible. Meanwhile we suggest you to keep calling the contact on your PIR and ask for an update.
Best regards, Alessandra

@tanjamaier17 @wizzair That's great, Tanja,
We hope to welcome you on board soon.
Best regards, Alessandra

@ja_le_c Hi there, 
We are sorry that you had difficulty contacting us by phone. Due to the current situation, unfortunately, all our channels are overloaded and there may be longer waiting times. How can we assist you?
Best regards, Shawn

@Geraldi70410580 Dear Geraldine,
We are sorry you still haven't got an answer yet.  Right now we have a lot of inquiries. This is what causes such long waiting times. We will pass your reference number with a note of urgency on to our relevant colleagues. Thank you!
Best regards, Alessandra

@Clarissimata Hi Classandra, 
We are sorry that you had difficulty contacting us by phone. Due to the current situation, unfortunately, all our channels are overloaded and there may be longer waiting times. Send us your booking code as PM, so we can assist you further.
Best regards, Shawn

@tanjamaier17 @wizzair Hello Tanja,
hopefully, you have enjoyed your flight with us.
Best regards, Alessandra

@Casey_Haviland Hello Casey,
please send us your booking code so we can have a closer look at your reservation.
Best regards, Alessandra

@Davethesoviet Dear Dave,
we regret to inform you that a name change is not permitted.
Best regards, Alessandra

@Han0o0sh7 Hi,
there will be an aircraft change in this case.
Best regards, Alessandra

@GatteJess Hallo Jessica,
wir dürfen eine neue E-Mail Adresse in die Buchung eingeben aber aus Datenschutzgründen, dürfen wir Dich nur über die erste angegebene E-Mail Adresse kontaktieren.
Liebe Grüße, Alessandra

@NadiehClarkson Hello Nadieh,
Unfortunately we cannot tell you a specific time of response, since your case has to be handled by various different departments. Still, we can assure you that our colleagues are doing their best to get back to you with news soon!
Best regards, Alessandra

@Mandavity Hello Mand,
please send us your booking code so we can have a closer look at your reservation.
Best regards, Alessandra
